57.4	Quantum_of_Solace	Quantum of Solace	Quantum of Solace (2008) is the twenty-second James Bond film, produced by Eon Productions for MGM and Columbia Pictures, and is the direct sequel to the 2006 film Casino Royale. Directed by Marc Forster, it features Daniel Craig's second performance as James Bond. In the film, Bond battles wealthy businessman Dominic Greene , a member of the Quantum organisation, posing as an environmentalist who intends to stage a coup d'Ã©tat in Bolivia to seize control of the nation's water supply. Bond seeks revenge for the death of his lover, Vesper Lynd (Eva Green), and is assisted by Camille Montes (Olga Kurylenko), who is also seeking revenge.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/61/Qos-teaser.jpg/220px-Qos-teaser.jpg
